summary: The phandom is a funny place. When you meet somebody who is in the phandom irl you immediately have something like a bond with...
body:
The phandom is a funny place. When you meet somebody who is in the phandom irl you immediately have something like a bond with them. Normally I avoid social interaction at all costs, but when I see someone with a ‘have the courage to exist’ shirt or other merch then that’ll be the one time that I go to the person to talk to them. Not only has Dan and Phil helped me to keep smiling when I feel down, the phandom has helped me as well. It’s just cool to see somebody that has a similar interest, high-five them and sometimes even hug them.

It’s an honour for me to be a part of this phandom and I hope that you all are having a great day and remember to keep smiling, because you only have one short life, so don’t waste it.
